      "y": -200,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 150,
      "color": "#a882ff",
      "text": "# Frontier AI \u2014 May 2026\n\nA multi-polar race: no single model wins every category. Four closed frontier labs trade the lead while open weights close the gap fast."
    },
    {
      "id": "g_anthropic",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -20,
      "y": 80,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 460,
      "color": "1",
      "label": "Anthropic"
    },
    {
      "id": "opus47",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 170,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## Claude Opus 4.7\n\nApr 16, 2026 \u00b7 #1 SWE-bench & MCP Atlas \u00b7 1M ctx (beta) \u00b7 $5 / $25 per MTok \u00b7 advanced SWE, long agents, hi-res vision."
    },
    {
      "id": "sonnet46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 360,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "### Claude Sonnet 4.6\n\nFeb 17 \u00b7 1M ctx \u00b7 near-Opus coding at ~60% cost."
    },
    {
      "id": "g_openai",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 80,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 460,
      "color": "5",
      "label": "OpenAI"
    },
    {
      "id": "gpt55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## GPT-5.5\n\nApr 23, 2026 \u00b7 first full retrain since GPT-4.5 \u00b7 1M ctx \u00b7 $5 / $30 \u00b7 leads Terminal-Bench & OSWorld \u00b7 native MCP."
    },
    {
      "id": "g_google",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 740,
      "y": 80,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 460,
      "color": "4",
      "label": "Google DeepMind"
    },
    {
      "id": "gemini31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 760,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## Gemini 3.1 Pro\n\nFeb 19, 2026 \u00b7 GPQA Diamond 94.3%, ARC-AGI-2 77.1% \u00b7 up to 2M ctx \u00b7 fully multimodal \u00b7 $1.25 / $5."
    },
    {
      "id": "g_xai",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 1120,
      "y": 80,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 460,
      "color": "2",
      "label": "xAI"
    },
    {
      "id": "grok420",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1140,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## Grok 4.20\n\nMar 10, 2026 \u00b7 2M ctx (largest) \u00b7 4-agent ensemble (Grok/Harper/Benjamin/Lucas) \u00b7 ~235 tok/s \u00b7 real-time X data."
    },
    {
      "id": "g_open",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 1500,
      "y": 80,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 460,
      "color": "3",
      "label": "Open weights"
    },
    {
      "id": "deepseek4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1520,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 170,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## DeepSeek V4-Pro\n\nApr 24, 2026 \u00b7 MIT open weights \u00b7 1.6T / 49B active MoE \u00b7 runs on Huawei Ascend \u00b7 1M ctx."
    },
    {
      "id": "glm51",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1520,
      "y": 360,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "### GLM-5.1\n\nMIT \u00b7 beat GPT-5.4 & Claude on SWE-bench Pro."
    },
    {
      "id": "trend",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 660,
      "y": 600,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 150,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "## What changed in 2026\n\nThe open\u2194closed gap shrank from 12\u201318 months (2024) to 3\u20136 months. Competition is now full-stack: model + tool use + runtime + governance."
    },
